<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />Yahweh, you have heard the needs of the oppressed;</para>

<para style="q1">you strengthen their heart, you listen to their prayer;</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />You defend the fatherless and the oppressed</para>

<para style="q1">so that no man on the earth will cause terror again.</para>
